text: El Hagounia () is a small town and rural commune in the Tarfaya Province of the Laâyoune-Sakia El Hamra region of the Moroccan-controlled part of Western Sahara. At the time of the 2014 census, the commune had a total population of 151 people. ==References== Category:Populated places in Laâyoune-Sakia El Hamra Category:Tarfaya
title: El Hagounia
